{"title":"春雨","authors":["董耀章"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董耀章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淅淅沥沥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一缕缕银线织成透明的轻纱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮闪闪，在天幕间飘逸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复苏了大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽开了桃李。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻纱中映出了农家小院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小院里满目生辉春光明丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选好的良种播撒在心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿夏金秋在人们心上流去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淅淅沥沥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻纱中映出了富饶的田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处春意盎然布满生机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁儿在飞，耙儿在追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛犊撒欢，马驹调皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风在垄沟里追逐嬉闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紫燕在蓝天下穿梭逗趣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点滴滴注心田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象灌了几斤槐花蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残雪顿消融，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光四处溢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的政策照人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天公随人意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淅淅沥沥……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}